Class DefaultWebSocketEventHandler

  • java.lang.Object
    • org.bluezoo.gumdrop.http.DefaultWebSocketEventHandler
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    WebSocketEventHandler
    public abstract class DefaultWebSocketEventHandler
extends java.lang.Object
implements WebSocketEventHandler
    A default implementation of WebSocketEventHandler with empty methods.

    Extend this class and override only the methods you need, rather than implementing all methods of the interface.

    Author:
    Chris Burdess

        Description copied from interface: WebSocketEventHandler
